Distrust
1) Any node can answer any request
2) Clients can recieve any file from any node
3) If a node fails to respond in time, then the client will try
   the next node, and so on.
4) Nodes can go offline without interuption to the system and also
   come online also without interuption to the system
5) Files will be distributed across nodes such that multiple nodes
   can fail without data loss or interuption of service